Package: APStatTools
Type: Package
Title: Making R easily usable for all AP and introductory level statistics computations for both teachers and students. 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Dustin", "Smith",
        email = "dusmith0@tamu.edu",
        role = "cre")
Maintainer: The package maintainer <dusmith0@tamu.edu>
Description: This package can function in place of the TI-Nspire or Desmos for all AP Statistics calculaitons. It also comes equipt
    with many real life data sets, animated similations, demonstrations, and methods for generating graphics and analysis. 
    This package aims to simplify the usage of R as much as possible for introductory level Statistics courses.  
